<br>
  &quot;want to come to fear &quot;<br>
<br>
I was sincere and I respond  something to the text of no thanks, but thank you for thinkin of me. ...<br>
<br>
<br>
just a bit later, I get another tell sumpin bout fear needing clerics...<br>
<br>
I was sincere and I respond  something to the text of no thanks, but thank you for thinkin of me. ...<br>
<br>
<br>
ok..so now it is close to midnight EST, my man is tired an needs sleep.<br>
Just as he camps, I load up Gate an just before its casted, I get a tell from a very good friend in Fear, askin me to please come an help. Since he is a dear friend, I have to at least make an attempt to help..I mean only like 3 golems up, how long can that actually take ? <br>
<br>
approx 10 min later I zone into fear and I make an <br>
/ooc its wabbit season<br>
<br>
at an attempt to add a bit of humor to the zone..<br>
 <br>
/ooc ok can i get camp location please <br>
<br>
 somebody /ooc back we are at Xcamp <br>
<br>
/ooc ok on my way<br>
<br>
...then the tells start,<br>
    can I get a rez please<br>
    can I get buffs, cleric in our group low on mana<br>
<br>
 ...giggles sigh, let me get to camp first ok <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <br>
<br>
/t Xperson would you know who has gems for clerics<br>
<br>
Xperson /t you Yperson should<br>
<br>
/t Yperson you have any gems for buffs<br>
<br>
Yperson /t you sure how many you need ?<br>
<br>
/t Yperson just five be good, please<br>
<br>
yperson  /t you oops sorry out, I will owe you<br>
<br>
/t yperson *sigh*<br>
<br>
<br>
Get in group, buff um up, mob pulled, casted CH's several times on group members, was down to approx 60 mana I believe..got pounded on, sham an cleric in group, not once did they heal me, an I did not drop fast, I was able to heal me with DL 2 times to try to keep me alive. asked in group, heal please ? ..sigh no heal, no response..<br>
<br>
....LOADING PLEASE WAIT <br>
<br>
Shrug, perhaps cleric n sham were afk when mob was pulled, will give them the benefit of the doubt, I guess.  Really felt unloved..sham an cleric in group an not one of them can cast heal on me..sigh...<br>
<br>
(..bound in NFP, yea my fault, I should have bound at portal. I figured 3 mobs, be easy no problem, why change bind point. ) <br>
 <br>
/who all Lillaane would show you I am in NFP..instead I am flooded with tells from others on  Fear raid..<br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp  &quot;can I get a rez &quot;, <br>
 &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &quot;rez me please&quot;, <br>
            &quot;players 1, 2, 4, 9, 15 all need rez&quot;<br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp ..etc..<br>
<br>
<br>
get a tell from another, everyone dead, I was able to camp out, let me know when to log on..ok so that tells me everyone on raid but one person dead, duh yea they all need rez'd. Granted my cleric has stick, but dang I am workin my way back to Fear, dont let your undies get all balled up. <br>
<br>
..and so the night continues, er early AM I should say<br>
<br>
<br>
Cuz this mob debuffs, ..<br>
we did dummy buffs, then after cleric buffs, druid in group does pack regen an thorns..ok somebody explain to me why when we have 4 dummy buffs up, whats up with pack regen huh?  yea like now I am thinkin sh*t ...ok so tanks have no resistance buffs they need now, got regen an thorns tho, have no haste up, no rune up, an druid just really pissed me off..how can pack regen really benefit on a mob..I mean explain to me, what is the purpose of this anyhoot ?<br>
<br>
its late, I am tired,<br>
* I have nothing to gain from this raid<br>
<br>
* nobody has the sense enuff in my group before with cleric   <br>
   an sham to heal the 59 cleric that is going down, and     <br>
   group member tell me I failed to heal them, duh why am I  <br>
   the dead one then, cuz casting heal others <br>
   increases argo on mobs..sigh<br>
<br>
*nobody has any gems, so I am  paying outta my pocket to  <br>
   buff groups up<br>
<br>
*being spam'd with rez's from others on raid, yes I can see  <br>
  your corpse way far off, maybe you could have your group  <br>
  member drag it back to camp and help me out here.<br>
<br>
*Died 3 times I think<br>
<br>
*group member died outside fear portal when we were  <br>
  running back in after a kind druid on raid gated us from NFP.<br>
<br>
*after the wizard mob was killed, seemed to be plane was <br>
   clear'd an most ppl were leaving.I did /ooc can I get a<br>
   gate out to Feerrott so I can rez  Xplayer that died <br>
   on fear portal. (this person was in my  <br>
  group on fear raid, yes came there to help) <br>
<br>
*hate to complain, 30 sec later ppl are leaving, plenty of  <br>
  druids an wizards there to start with..I am tired too, had <br>
  nothing to benefit from 3 deaths in fear ..came to help <br>
  these druids and wizards, why the hell should I have to beg <br>
  for one of them to gate me out, specially since I am   <br>
  wanting to go an rez a group member. <br>
<br>
* Nobody is polite enuff to realize that yes everyone needs <br>
   rez, damnit dont spam me, I am sorry I have enough tells  <br>
   goin on at once. <br>
<br>
**got a few thank yous after I rez'd them..in general tho, I felt <br>
  I was taken advantage of, some ppl were not pleasent there at <br>
    all. and Overall, not a thank you for coming to help on this <br>
   raid an stayin up until 4AM PST from anyone that had something <br>
  last night in fear. <br>
<br>
<br>
..I went there to help, because a very good friend asked me to go, not for any other reason at all, and I would go again <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  and again if that person was to ask me...and except for my guild member and my dear friend, nobody even cared<br>
about a thank you.<br>
<br>
Glad the wizard got the epic part an the 7 dr00ds or so there all seemed to have got something before I called it a night. Not sure who else got any drops. I just have one more thing to add tho, I do not ever mind coming to help dont get me wrong here...<br>
<br>
Dont spam clerics for res's..they will get to them as best they can. Believe it there is really an order in which classes are to be rez'd.  I believe in my opinion it is like this..<br>
<br>
**Cleric, monk/rog to pull corpses if need be, enchanter, bard, mag, necro, etc. Think about those classes an  you will understand why.<br>
<br>
 Dont spam the cleric to rez you, we do our best to get everyone as best an fast as we can, trust me or you will result in getting a pissed off cleric very fast. And, you should be sure to thank them for coming to fear to help you get your epic, drops or armor drops when they are there for no benefit of their own. I did not place any names in this rave, cuz that does not matter. Point I was tryin to make<br>
was that ppl go to help others in this game, try to remember your maners.<br>
<br>
 Does this mean that I will have to beg wizards an dr00ds on that raid for a gate next time I see them, naw, I wouldnt step so low. They could return the kind favor though an offer to gate me, even free, when I do a /shout payin 50pp for gate.<br>
